subject: Make email not dependent on ecore_x.
commitMessage:
Make email not dependent on ecore_x.

Here we have the function _composer_create_sub_window() that was highly dependent
on ecore-x but was never used. So, all the dependent code was removed. When
someone bring this function back to life, he can make a new version independent
of the display server.

Change-Id: I7fa073e8724cc78cebd690720bb802db9601c100
Signed-off-by: Leandro Dorileo <leandro.maciel.dorileo@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Fabio Mello <fabio.mello@intel.com>
